 >> `A2 INTER B IN events p` by METIS_TAC [EVENTS_INTER]
 >> `(A1 DIFF A2) INTER B IN events p` by METIS_TAC [EVENTS_INTER, EVENTS_DIFF]
 >> `prob p (A2 INTER B) + prob p ((A1 DIFF A2) INTER B) =
